---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Research Strategy | Brenkley Doctoral College" description="Brenkley Doctoral College's research strategy — our vision for practitioner-led inquiry, research priorities, and our commitment to impact-driven scholarship.">

  <section class="bg-surface border-b border-border py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="section-label mb-4">Research</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Research Strategy 2024–2028</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">Brenkley Doctoral College's research strategy sets out our vision for practitioner-led doctoral inquiry — what we aim to produce, how we aim to produce it, and the impact we intend to have on professional practice and organisational life.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Vision -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <p class="section-label mb-3">Vision</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Research Vision</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <p class="text-muted mb-4">Brenkley Doctoral College's research vision is to be the leading institution in the UK for practitioner-led doctoral inquiry — research that originates in professional practice, is executed with academic rigour, and returns knowledge to the professional communities that need it.</p>
          <p class="text-muted mb-4">We are not aiming to replicate the research model of traditional universities. We are building something different: an institution where the research questions come from the inside of organisations, where methodology is selected for fitness of purpose rather than fashion, and where the test of a study's value is not only whether it gets published but whether it changes how organisations work.</p>
          <p class="text-muted">This does not mean abandoning academic standards. Brenkley Doctoral College research is peer-reviewed, theoretically grounded, and methodologically defensible. We hold our researchers to the same standards of rigour, integrity, and critical thought that any doctoral institution should expect. What we add to those standards is a commitment to relevance — to producing knowledge that matters beyond the academy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="card border-l-4 border-accent">
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Practitioner-Led</h3>
            <p class="text-muted text-sm">Research questions originate in professional experience. Our researchers bring the questions; we provide the frameworks, methods, and rigour to address them properly.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card border-l-4 border-accent">
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Academically Rigorous</h3>
            <p class="text-muted text-sm">All Brenkley Doctoral College research meets the standards expected of doctoral-level scholarship — theoretical grounding, methodological justification, ethical integrity, and critical analysis.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card border-l-4 border-accent">
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Impact-Oriented</h3>
            <p class="text-muted text-sm">We measure success not only by academic output but by the practical consequences of our research — changed practices, improved systems, better outcomes for organisations and the people within them.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Priorities -->
  <section class="bg-surface border-y border-border py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <p class="section-label mb-3">Priorities</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Research Priorities 2024–2028</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="card">
          <span class="tag tag-doctoral mb-3 inline-block">Priority 1</span>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Leadership and Governance</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">Support a significant body of doctoral research examining leadership effectiveness, board governance, strategic decision-making, and the management of organisational complexity across private, public, and third sectors.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <span class="tag tag-doctoral mb-3 inline-block">Priority 2</span>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Technology, Organisations, and Work</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">Build a cluster of research examining how digital transformation, AI adoption, and platform-mediated work are changing organisations — and what leaders need to know and do in response.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <span class="tag tag-doctoral mb-3 inline-block">Priority 3</span>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Sustainability and Responsible Practice</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">Develop research on sustainability strategy, climate-resilient leadership, responsible innovation, and ethical business conduct — connecting organisational practice to wider societal responsibilities.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <span class="tag tag-doctoral mb-3 inline-block">Priority 4</span>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Professional Education and Development</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">Advance knowledge on how professionals learn, develop, and maintain expertise over careers — including leadership development, professional identity, and the design of effective development interventions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <span class="tag tag-doctoral mb-3 inline-block">Priority 5</span>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Practitioner-Research Methodology</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">Continue to develop and disseminate methodological knowledge specific to practitioner-research — insider positionality, the ethics of organisational research, and the design of rigorous professional doctorate studies.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <span class="tag tag-doctoral mb-3 inline-block">Priority 6</span>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Workforce Wellbeing and Human Capital</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">Support research on employee wellbeing, talent management, diversity and inclusion, and the management conditions that enable people to flourish and perform in professional environments.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Impact -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <p class="section-label mb-3">Impact</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Our Impact Goals</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent mb-2">30+</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Doctoral completions</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">Target: thirty or more doctoral completions by 2028, contributing original knowledge across our six research priority areas.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent mb-2">15+</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Peer-reviewed publications</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">Fifteen or more peer-reviewed journal articles from Brenkley Doctoral College-affiliated researchers, including supervisors and doctoral graduates, by 2028.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent mb-2">5+</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Policy contributions</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">Five or more documented instances of Brenkley Doctoral College research informing policy, professional standards, or sector-level practice by 2028.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-surface border-t border-border py-16 px-6 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Be part of the research community</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-8">Join a growing community of practitioner-scholars generating knowledge that matters. Explore our research themes or apply to a Brenkley Doctoral College programme.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap">
        <a href="/research/themes" class="btn-primary">Research themes</a>
        <a href="/apply" class="btn-outline">Apply to Brenkley Doctoral College</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
